src:
Watch: The Best of Beto’s Failed Presidential Campaign
02 Nov 2019, 00:47 by Matt Perdie
A look back at many of the hallmark moments made by former Democratic presidential candidate Robert Francis O’Rourke who dropped out of the 2020 presidential race on Friday.
